https://www.youtube.com/c/GospelProductionsbyJoeHackney
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters' Karaoke youtube!

In this "My Tribute" song, I sing about how grateful I am to God for everything He's done for me. 
I hope you enjoy this karaoke song as much as I do! If you'd like to hear more of my music, please visit my YouTube channel and subscribe to my channel for updates! Thank you for watching!
